## 16. Post-script gates (v2.9.0)

### Que son

Los gates validan que el YAML producido por un script Python tenga el contenido esperado, no solo que el exit code sea 0. Esto cierra el GAP #5.3 del INTEGRATION-VERDICT.md: "Silent failures en scripts Python".

### 11 gates configurados

| Script | Que valida | on_fail |
|---|---|---|
| `collect_evidence.py` | items (min 1) + hash_chain (min 64 chars) | block |
| `score_evidence.py` | score (0-1) + metrics dict | warn |
| `generate_plan.py` | unidades (min 1) + topological_sort | block |
| `predict_impact.py` | predictions list | warn |
| `scaffold_impl.py` | files_to_create + files_to_modify | warn |
| `index_codebase.py` | files (min 1) | block |
| `code_quality.py` | total_files | warn |
| `test_coverage.py` | coverage_percentage (0-100) | warn |
| `vulnerability_scanner.py` | total_findings + tools_used | warn |
| `code_smells.py` | summary dict | warn |
| `full_audit.py` | summary.final_score (0-100) + summary.grade | warn |

### Acciones

- **pass**: todos los checks pasaron, el loop engine avanza normalmente
- **warn**: algunos checks fallaron pero no son criticos, el loop engine avanza con warning
- **block**: checks criticos fallaron, el loop engine NO avanza de fase

### Como usar

```bash
# Inicializar configuracion con defaults
python3 scripts/python/post_script_gates.py init --repo-root .

# Listar gates
python3 scripts/python/post_script_gates.py list --repo-root .

# Validar un YAML contra el gate del script
python3 scripts/python/post_script_gates.py check \
    --repo-root . \
    --script collect_evidence.py \
    --output plan/active/APOLO-X/evidence/EVIDENCE-PACK.yaml

# Validar todos los artifacts de un flow
python3 scripts/python/post_script_gates.py check-all --repo-root . --flowid APOLO-X

# Habilitar/deshabilitar un gate
python3 scripts/python/post_script_gates.py enable --repo-root . --script scaffold_impl.py
python3 scripts/python/post_script_gates.py disable --repo-root . --script code_quality.py
```

### Ejemplo de salida

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "script": "collect_evidence.py",
  "enabled": true,
  "on_fail": "block",
  "all_checks_pass": false,
  "checks": [
    {
      "path": "items",
      "status": "FAIL",
      "error": "list length 0 < min_length 1",
      "value_preview": "[]",
      "description": "Al menos 1 item de evidencia"
    },
    {
      "path": "hash_chain",
      "status": "FAIL",
      "error": "string length 5 < min_length 64",
      "value_preview": "short",
      "description": "SHA-256 hash chain"
    }
  ],
  "action": "block",
  "yaml_path": "plan/active/APOLO-X/evidence/EVIDENCE-PACK.yaml",
  "status": "fail"
}
```

