### v2.8.0 (2026-06-21) — Vulnerability Scanning + Code Smells + Dead Code + Full Audit

**Novedades:**

- **`vulnerability_scanner.py`** (NEW) — Escaneo de vulnerabilidades CVE:
  - safety (Python)
  - npm audit (Node)
  - pip-audit (Python alternativo)
  - govulncheck (Go)
  - cargo audit (Rust)
  - Output: `VULNERABILITY-REPORT.yaml` con total_findings, tools_used, tools_unavailable

- **`code_smells.py`** (NEW) — Deteccion de code smells + dead code:
  - Long methods (>50 lineas)
  - God classes (>10 metodos)
  - Deep nesting (>4 niveles)
  - Code duplication (>80% similaridad)
  - Dead code (funciones/clases nunca referenciadas)
  - Complejidad ciclomatica nativa (radon, gocyclo, regex fallback)
  - Output: `CODE-SMELLS.yaml` con summary.total_smells, dead_code, high_complexity

- **`full_audit.py`** (NEW) — Auditoria completa en 11 pasos:
  1. Code index (AST)
  2. Code quality (bandit, radon, eslint-security, gosec, cppcheck)
  3. Vulnerability scan (safety, npm audit, pip-audit, govulncheck, cargo audit)
  4. Code smells (long methods, god classes, deep nesting, duplication)
  5. Dead code analysis
  6. Cyclomatic complexity
  7. Test coverage
  8. LSP diagnostics
  9. Cross-language analysis
  10. Function summaries
  11. Refactoring suggestions
  - Output: `FULL-AUDIT-REPORT.yaml` con summary.final_score (0-100) y grade (A-F)

- **`cross_language_analyzer.py`** (NEW) — Mapea calls entre lenguajes
- **`summarize_functions.py`** (NEW) — Genera docstrings para funciones sin documentar
- **`code_generator.py`** (NEW) — Generacion de codigo en 8 lenguajes
- **`doc_generator.py`** (NEW) — Generacion de documentacion (README sections, API docs)
- **`project_templates.py`** (NEW) — 8 plantillas de proyecto (Next.js, Go API, Python CLI, etc.)
- **`onboarding.py`** (NEW) — Wizard interactivo para configurar el plugin
- **`github_actions.py`** (NEW) — Genera workflows CI/CD automaticamente

